thread.title: Pamela
thread.title_full: NorthShore Care Supply reviewed by Pamela

author: Pamela
title: Pamela
text: I had ordered some diapers from NorthShore through Amazon, but when I contacted NorthShore directly I was extremely pleased with the advice I received about choices, and I think their own products that I purchased have been better than commercial brands previously purchased. I will definitely remain a customer.
